MERGE INTO `default`.duplicate_keys_standard AS l
	USING flow_temp_store_table_1 AS r
	ON l.id = r.id::BIGINT

	AND r._metadata_file_name IN ('1_56d95480-3230-46c2-aca0-370c9caf1644_store.json')
	WHEN MATCHED AND r.flow_document <=> NULL THEN
		DELETE
	WHEN MATCHED THEN
		UPDATE SET l.flow_published_at = r.flow_published_at::TIMESTAMP
, l.int = r.int::BIGINT
, l.str = r.str
, l.flow_document = r.flow_document
	WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
		INSERT (id, flow_published_at, int, str, flow_document)
		VALUES (r.id::BIGINT
, r.flow_published_at::TIMESTAMP
, r.int::BIGINT
, r.str
, r.flow_document
);
